dcterms:description: The TAQ dataset provides detailed tick-by-tick trade and quote data encompassing all transactions in the U.S. National Market System and delivers transaction data on an intraday basis, down to the microsecond, spanning more than 10,000 stock issues across 16 major American exchanges such as the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE), American Stock Exchange (AMEX), and Nasdaq.
dcterms:title: NYSE Trade and Quote (TAQ) dataset
